    <h2>2012 Training Course in MCH Epidemiology</h2>
		  <p><img src="../../images/epidemiology-1.jpg" alt="Epidemiology" class="right border">The MCHB at HRSA and CDC offered this Training Course in MCH Epidemiology in 2012 as part of their ongoing effort to enhance the analytic capacity of state and local health agencies. </p>
		  <p>This national program was aimed primarily at professionals in state and local health agencies who have significant responsibility for collecting, processing, analyzing, and reporting maternal and child health data. The course was geared to individuals with intermediate to advanced skills in using statistical and epidemiologic methods, preferably in MCH or a related field.</p>
		 
